name: Driving Games Precision Parking Drive Luxury Limo Jeep Racing School
name_original: Driving Games Precision Parking Drive Luxury Limo Jeep Racing School
description:
Are you crazy about parking games?? Love to drive your car and take up the ultimate driving challenge?

Then Driving Games Precision Parking is the best car parking simulator for you! Hop into your car and explore the city with very less spaces to park! Rush to the spot and park before your time runs out or the space is gone!
Be careful while you drive in this crazy car parking game - Driving Games Precision Parking, do not hit any obstacles or you may trash your car!
Explore the wonderful 3D city in your lovely little car. If your ever get bored, earn the rewards to upgrade your car for the best car simulation experience.Filled with 15 nail biting engrossing levels.
